<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 21:14:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>秘鲁中国建造的大型港口将于11月开始每周运输两艘集装箱船</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/perus-chinese-built-mega-port-begin-moving-two-container-ships-week-november-2024-10-18/</link><description>秘鲁大型钱凯港运营商中国远洋海运集团的一位高管周五表示，继该港口于 11 月中旬落成后，该港口将于下个月下旬开始每周运送两艘集装箱船。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 20:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/perus-chinese-built-mega-port-begin-moving-two-container-ships-week-november-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>WTA综述：俄罗斯选手达里亚·卡萨特金娜、米拉·安德烈耶娃在中国闯入半决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wta-roundup-russians-daria-kasatkina-mirra-andreeva-reach-semis-china-2024-10-18/</link><description>周五，俄罗斯五号种子达莉亚·卡萨特金娜在决胜局挽救两个赛点，以6-4、1-6、7-6(6)击败尤利娅·普廷塞娃，晋级中国宁波公开赛半决赛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 18:22:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wta-roundup-russians-daria-kasatkina-mirra-andreeva-reach-semis-china-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>英国表示外长与中国外长的会晤具有建设性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-says-foreign-ministers-meeting-with-chinese-counterpart-was-constructive-2024-10-18/</link><description>英国周五称外交部长戴维·拉米与中国外交部长王毅的会晤具有建设性，并表示双方致力于保持两国之间的公开对话。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 15:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-says-foreign-ministers-meeting-with-chinese-counterpart-was-constructive-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国钢铁出口将持续增加，有可能加剧贸易摩擦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/elevated-china-steel-exports-set-persist-threaten-worsen-trade-friction-2024-10-18/</link><description>业内人士和分析师表示，中国钢铁制造商的出口量已经达到近十年来的高位，预计到 2025 年将继续推迟出货量，以应对产能过剩和国内需求疲软的问题，这可能会加剧日益加剧的贸易摩擦。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 09:15:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/elevated-china-steel-exports-set-persist-threaten-worsen-trade-friction-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>投资者买入中国股票，然后等待时机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/investors-buy-then-bide-time-china-2024-10-18/</link><description>在出现经济改善的具体迹象之前，很少有人愿意大规模投资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 08:15:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/investors-buy-then-bide-time-china-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国国家主席习近平将赴俄罗斯出席金砖国家领导人会晤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-president-xi-attend-brics-summit-russia-2024-10-18/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，中国国家主席习近平将于10月22日至24日出席在俄罗斯喀山举行的金砖国家领导人第十六次会晤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 07:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-president-xi-attend-brics-summit-russia-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>Counterpoint 称，苹果新款 iPhone 在中国的前 3 周销量猛增 20%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-new-iphone-sales-china-jump-20-first-3-weeks-counterpoint-says-2024-10-18/</link><description>研究公司 Counterpoint 的数据显示，苹果公司的新款 iPhone 在中国开局强劲，自推出以来的前三周销量较 2023 年机型增长了 20%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 07:39:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-new-iphone-sales-china-jump-20-first-3-weeks-counterpoint-says-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，中国回收集团第一次会议在天津召开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-national-recycling-group-holds-first-meeting-tianjin-xinhua-reports-2024-10-18/</link><description>据官方新华社周五报道，华润循环集团成立大会在中国北部的天津举行，中国推进了建立国家循环利用集团的计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 06:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-national-recycling-group-holds-first-meeting-tianjin-xinhua-reports-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>香港迎来近两年来最繁忙的IPO周，中国的刺激措施给交易撮合者带来希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-marks-busiest-ipo-week-nearly-two-years-with-china-stimulus-giving-2024-10-18/</link><description>香港迎来了近两年来新股发行最繁忙的一周，融资额高达 13 亿美元，这让银行家和投资者相信两年来的股票销售冻结可能会有所缓解。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 05:14:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-marks-busiest-ipo-week-nearly-two-years-with-china-stimulus-giving-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出1120亿美元融资计划提振股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-kicks-off-112-billion-funding-schemes-support-stock-market-2024-10-18/</link><description>中国人民银行详细说明了 9 月底首次宣布的互换和再贷款计划的操作细节。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 03:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-kicks-off-112-billion-funding-schemes-support-stock-market-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行行长暗示进一步降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-cenbank-chief-warns-against-any-illegal-fund-flows-into-stock-market-2024-10-18/</link><description>中国央行行长周五表示，根据流动性状况，商业银行存款准备金率可能在年底前进一步下调 25 至 50 个基点，为采取更多政策宽松措施敞开大门。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 03:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-cenbank-chief-warns-against-any-illegal-fund-flows-into-stock-market-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>台积电盈利超预期，股价再创新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-stock-hits-new-high-after-posting-forecast-beating-earnings-2024-10-18/</link><description>全球最大的代工芯片制造商台积电发布了超出预期的第三季度盈利，并对强劲的人工智能 (AI) 需求做出了乐观的展望，周五，在台北上市的台积电股价创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 02:28:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-stock-hits-new-high-after-posting-forecast-beating-earnings-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国9月工业产出增长5.4% 超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-september-industrial-output-rises-54-beating-expectations-2024-10-18/</link><description>中国 9 月份工业产出同比增长 5.4%，高于 8 月份的 4.5%，这给政策制定者带来了一些鼓励，因为他们在年底临近时加大了重振低迷经济的力度。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 02:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-september-industrial-output-rises-54-beating-expectations-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国开展调查了解“生育恐惧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-launches-survey-understand-fear-having-children-2024-10-18/</link><description>在当局努力提高低迷的出生率之际，中国国家卫生健康委员会 (NHC) 正在对 3 万人进行调查，以了解影响他们对生育态度的因素以及“对生孩子的恐惧”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 01:49:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-launches-survey-understand-fear-having-children-2024-10-18/</guid></item><item><title>油价下跌，因中国需求困境和中东前景喜忧参半，每周下跌 7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-edges-up-track-biggest-weekly-loss-over-month-2024-10-18/</link><description>周五石油期货下跌，一周跌幅超过 7%，此前数据显示中国经济增长放缓，投资者消化了中东地区前景喜忧参半的情况。</description><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 00:33:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-edges-up-track-biggest-weekly-loss-over-month-2024-10-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>